  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<String>, PrefixConfig

    public final class DynamicPrefixConfig
extends DefaultPrefixConfig
    The Class DynamicPrefixConfig will take any kind of Prefix and add it as a known prefix list.
